{"tid":1442090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地做唔做到比對家更團結???","createTime":"2019-08-10T22:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:03.000Z","uid":295341,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9c99fa2b77899c61b19c5f328b2201114d0f894c","tid":1442090,"uid":295341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:31:10.000Z","msg":"對家有一點我好佩服,就係好撚團結,<br />\n唔理件事岩定錯,目標一致,好少有分化, <br />\n極其量都係老鼠芬屌777, <br />\n何妖發隊友皮氣同777話暫緩之後保皇有少少割蓆既情況...到最近就有元秋出post 話對777失望...<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地好似好快就可以解決矛盾, <br />\n跟住槍口又再次一致對外....<br />\n黑狗做錯野都繼續讚...<br />\n呢方面我地真係要學下...雖然口講錫春袋都唔割...<br />\n但周不時都見到d post <br />\n又鬼又分化呢樣唔做得果樣失民意失焦咁...<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇諗下可以盲目少少,<br />\n勇武又好和理非又好冷氣軍師又好...<br />\n當大家係結拜兄弟咁互相死撑,比對家更團結呀...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ead5905a322ab290db7f815eed3cebc7db9bea2","tid":1442090,"uid":295341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af51a73fbc395045d4758b8ad16dadb4c8325a00","tid":1442090,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:36:52.000Z","msg":"宣密密做 落場手足可唔可以都幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑狗屌老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442071</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0f5bf1cac6b98383150e4bc1e7fc0cf4ad0df22e","tid":1442090,"uid":295341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2"},{"pid":"6497a62b01520c433eee649d90933b0598c1ab3b","tid":1442090,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:41:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8983cdf656ad4b7e235b0c32e41e1990677a3653","tid":1442090,"uid":205972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:41:28.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆<br />\n兄弟爬山 團結一致"},{"pid":"d89a2137af6f77670bd6f07228bb5e170f5aa328","tid":1442090,"uid":282328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:43:51.000Z","msg":"永不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ca2efe032e573492bfd415d24ac201c6381dc5","tid":1442090,"uid":295341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />3"},{"pid":"61b303f9bd0f85a950a21509aec48284ce86523c","tid":1442090,"uid":270912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:52:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7102f45060d2f52b7fca257dc28627e6d8d11bb","tid":1442090,"uid":89179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:59:11.000Z","msg":"其實某程度上因為佢地好撚蠢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以容易被人煽動而唔去思考當中有咩問題<br />\n但我地手足唔同 個個都有獨立思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有意見會提出討論 睇落好似無咁團結<br />\n但咁先至係我地不斷進步嘅原因 <br />\n我地要繼續加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆<br />\n無忘721 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"155f8e29d4ddb6738c2c50a1f6df1f9291b07f56","tid":1442090,"uid":14305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c43eead9d16cafb15c9c1753d849800a84531f1","tid":1442090,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:08:51.000Z","msg":"因為對家好多鬼混佐入來不停搞分化<br />\n目的係要動搖軍心，大家唔好俾佢哋呃到<br />\n同埋我哋都可以去對方陣地分化下佢哋"},{"pid":"287abe3a81698e62a5e8342b01242089599c644d","tid":1442090,"uid":295341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T00:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe9ab931a6c2d0ab47ed30fc1cbb2a5efabbd6f","tid":1442090,"uid":130996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T00:18:42.000Z","msg":"佢地有共同利益，所以可以咁團結<br />\n我地只有共同信念<br />\n要保持前線掉核彈都唔撚割既諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102ee683e4d99999fb8a9ef573251fbb34b86881","tid":1442090,"uid":295341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:42:31.000Z","msg":"大家團結d 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明人數可以以10圍1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba12d6df549b993a68a5acf4ba505f40eef16b02","tid":1442090,"uid":295341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:20.000Z","msg":"自推😭跪求唔好分化呀大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325dc3f24ba9eebdc6f7cfe9ade2d3254d403811","tid":1442090,"uid":295341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:38.